{"tid":1313960,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[沙田jj]沙田真係好多商場同天橋","createTime":"2019-07-14T03:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T05:16:33.000Z","uid":1582,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"71f41926c39a4d87ad783a4bf3600e5115cb209d","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"講下新城市大約地圖<br />\n<br />\n火車站嗰座叫一期<br />\n一共有八層<br />\n八樓：酒樓<br />\n七樓：餐廳/空中花園<br />\n<br />\n五至八樓都係冇得走出去 <br />\n四樓只可以連接去連城廣場 即係火車站個商場 <br />\n連城廣場有個平台落客站 即係火車站巴士總站既樓上 <br />\n另外可以連接去新城市廣場三期 即係一田嗰邊<br />\n<br />\n三樓可以連接去沙田中心 好運中心 偉華中心 沙田大會堂平台 戲院仲有電梯連接三樓同地下小賣部 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n二樓就係 Citysuper  冇得走<br />\n一樓就唔使講啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把門口<br />\n<br />\n新城市三期又連住希爾頓中心同帝都酒店 大把出入口<br />\n<br />\n而好運中心沙田中心就喺沙田街市嗰面有天橋行去瀝源邨 而瀝源邨又有天橋連去禾輋邨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74f4bc51007bd4e21adbfbe86af6f5df507f331","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:43:38.000Z","msg":"由大圍去到第一城<br />\n足足有八條橋可以跨越城門河 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781920a15325577ef1eef5d5cbf593fca86a87c3","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:45:22.000Z","msg":"由市中心過到對面河 沿住河邊一路行<br />\n行到去馬鞍山都仲得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過小心啦 河邊平時都好多人放狗"},{"pid":"ca0403a72062da8bfff1f7d221d54311689c066a","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"有冇沙田地膽一齊講下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac816f9781bdbd08d2c769db1726904b0529bbb","tid":1313960,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:50:20.000Z","msg":"全部同我入黎！教你下一步點做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1313709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1313709</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33c4cec74c779d5f1aae8f71721754ad38e9edc4","tid":1313960,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:51:56.000Z","msg":"行隧道可往荃灣"},{"pid":"95fb0c35e023bb69257c0a909755357d6fd3fb67","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AdJqTkQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdJqTkQ.png&h=28620238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍色就大圍<br />\n黃色就對面河<br />\n紅色就瀝源邨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46a69c1732c0ee17e49f55acea4e764460f1a46","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"大家喺沙田唔識路可以問下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260cb032e1743f802623f7a7f0c752258f3817a1","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:57:50.000Z","msg":"沙田 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ee2c7247cdf08f86405c828a424efaf99d48f7","tid":1313960,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b411f3a5322da0c8a468ef015ff1ed35426662a1","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:58:35.000Z","msg":"我就唔信佢咁多條路都有狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3dfe2674abf410741d0531c339d2c9697d1349","tid":1313960,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"沙田政府合署宜家家私地形真係不利架 <br />\n上水金鐘都係唔問題"},{"pid":"2ece26ac6abea92277412fd81012fe9fc4fd8ee7","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沙田大圍真係好多單車舖<br />\n大家行完唔想行 做下運動租部單車踩都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假日好多人踩單車 大埔還車都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"29d531af0ad4b49ac766f0d48bd4a6896b9be0d3","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實沙田真係好有趣 穿嚟穿去好多小路穿去其他地方<br />\n一時三刻諗唔晒喺度講 落場同各位巴絲再講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家入嚟分享一下"},{"pid":"da4620f926d13a00e7431f591a401aeef3754f01","tid":1313960,"uid":52341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:03:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"886b8d09a999f3596dbafe8c9c4db9b2b830822e","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9c3dfe2674abf410741d0531c339d2c9697d1349","tid":1313960,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"沙田政府合署宜家家私地形真係不利架 <br />\n上水金鐘都係唔問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:07:23.000Z","msg":"所以大家醒水啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9e19f0930a025a8425f236c2cf1ac24547ead9","tid":1313960,"uid":201159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"三期裝修喎<br />\n依家啲路又窄同埋得一條路過到希爾頓<br />\n唔好入三期"},{"pid":"86492d49afda8ad210e705c71113268a2504a8f2","tid":1313960,"uid":1582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9e19f0930a025a8425f236c2cf1ac24547ead9","tid":1313960,"uid":201159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T04:07:51.000Z","msg":"三期裝修喎<br />\n依家啲路又窄同埋得一條路過到希爾頓<br />\n唔好入三期"},"citedBy":